name: Paris Passport Invitation Prints
description:
This adorable passport invitation will definitely set the tone for your Paris-themed birthday party, shower, Sweet 16 party or even for a wedding. The invitation allows you to use up to 5 photos.

Passport invitations require a 50 minimum print order.

Requests for other quantities are welcome.

**At the moment, we are only shipping within the U.S.

Invitations will arrive professionally printed on 100lb. matte cover stock and each are sized 4.25" x 6" (when folded). They will also be scored and folded, in addition to having rounded corners. White pink or black envelopes are included.

Along with your order information, submit the following information by clicking on the "Contact" button located on the lower right-hand side of the page:

1. First and Last Name
2. Age (if this is for a shower, skip this)
3. Birthday or Wedding Date
4. Date and Time of Party
5. Event Location (Address)
6. RSVP Information
7. Wording for the circle text design seen on the cover
8. Name for the "Authorized Signature" line that is in
the inside cover of the invitation
9. Misc. Information - City the person was born or location
of wedding.

PHOTOS:
Up to five photos can be used in this invitation. Please upload your high resolution photos (300 DPI) via this link https://www.yousendit.com/dropbox?dropbox=FLIPAWOO.

FLIPAWOO is not responsible for any poor quality photos.

COLORS:
Colors can be changed (up to two) without any additional charge. Please keep in mind that colors you see on computer monitors may not look exactly the same in prints. If the colors seem off to you in your test prints (proof), please let me know so that I can change them to your satisfaction.

PROOF:
A low resolution file proof will be sent to the e-mail address on your Etsy account within 24-48 hours after the above requested information is submitted. Be sure to check for any errors before approving. FLIPAWOO will not be responsible for any errors after the file proof has been approved.

PRINTED INVITATIONS:
Please allow up to 10-12 business days after approving the digital proof for the order to arrive. If ordering with rounded corners, wait up to 5 extra business days for arrival.

TERMS: All files from FLIPAWOO are for personal-use only and should not be distributed and shared. Resale of the files as a digital and printed document in any form for any digital and printed medium are strictly prohibited.

Due to the nature of this order, no refunds will be made.
